{"tid":1178364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（中國人最愛連登）京東：在香港知名討論區如連登、親子王國宣傳","createTime":"2019-05-30T10:59:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T13:18:43.000Z","uid":50275,"like":4,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"0c8b9073239f15d622c488e04bf88becbb6cc755","tid":1178364,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T10:59:28.000Z","msg":"img]<a href=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190529/large/1559122060_dc1b.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190529%2Flarge%2F1559122060_dc1b.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=UJpThwxvwmp1Vrh6wv1Q1abKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=52fb8be6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190529/large/1559122060_dc1b.jpg[/img]</a> <br />\n<br />\n京東宣佈，「618年中購物節」於本周六(6月1日)啟動，京東全球售業務負責人王珍指，今年商品數目超過5,000萬件，推出社交拼購、免郵總額超過5,000萬元（人民幣．下同）。公司十分重視香港市場，目標是香港銷售額按年升三倍。<br />\n<br />\n有記者問到中美貿易戰對購物節的影響，王珍表示由於送到美國的運費較高，加上電壓、插座不同，所以售到美國的貨品一向較少，貿易戰影響輕微，公司在澳洲、俄羅斯等地亦會積極部署。<br />\n<br />\n近日亦有指華為新手機P30二手價急跌，有記者問是否受到近日華為事件影響，旗下手機因此會割價促銷。王珍指P30賣得不錯，但對於近日華為手機在中國的銷售情況就不便回應，只補充6月11日將會有大牌手機5折優惠。記者亦到京東商城查看華為P30的情況，與其他網店相若，暫未見有大幅減價。<br />\n<br />\n王珍亦指，與騰訊（700）旗下WeChat作為購物節的宣傳平台，並針對香港市場，會在Google、Facebook，同時亦會尋找KOL，以及在香港知名討論區如連登（LIHKG）、親子王國宣傳，她指京東一向主打高品質正貨，正好符合親子王國網民對貨品有較高要求。以數量計，香港區食品的銷量最多，當中包括海底撈火鍋、乾果、大米等。<br />\n<br />\n京東亦指，購物節期間亦會為香港用戶設包郵優惠，6月1日至20日，自營商品購物滿199元，10公斤內免運費，另外亦會與VISA及HKT拍住賞Mastercard推優惠券，香港區平均2.5個工作天就可以送到。"},{"pid":"54edb8e34fdbdee0841107a7015fe692d4dde9a5","tid":1178364,"uid":28068,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T11:00:45.000Z","msg":"可以點樣係lihkg宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f1657b4ee23fc0eba95c586648f1dcc154f3c2","tid":1178364,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T11:05:47.000Z","msg":"【618購物節】京東：在連登設廣告宣傳 港人最愛買海底撈<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cGJCfT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cGJCfT</a><br />\n#2 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ff95a3c157d20216a708a34788811e2cc3689f3f","tid":1178364,"uid":191815,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T11:07:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n王珍亦指，與騰訊（700）旗下WeChat作為購物節的宣傳平台，並針對香港市場，會在Google、Facebook，<strong>同時亦會尋找KOL，以及在香港知名討論區如連登（LIHKG）</strong>、親子王國宣傳</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">𠵱鋪搵達哥就掂曬啦 佢想食北水 連登仔又個個Buy</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea2f055a4106a6558278e3d03885f20aa6ab9f7","tid":1178364,"uid":150609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T11:07:58.000Z","msg":"有冇免運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9199e83d80bfee17c3c087c2cc2d69baf6d87b88","tid":1178364,"uid":198855,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T11:08:56.000Z","msg":"京東<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連內地人都會叫京東做 <strong>二手東</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a7902c6cba22a43c09262b2d1b1a9e511c54cc9","tid":1178364,"uid":58247,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"54edb8e34fdbdee0841107a7015fe692d4dde9a5","tid":1178364,"uid":28068,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T11:00:45.000Z","msg":"可以點樣係lihkg宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T11:08:59.000Z","msg":"我諗連登主動宣傳任何野都係地獄級難度"},{"pid":"f78911a67677ec1613514bf4e2bb983c6a95fe79","tid":1178364,"uid":5218,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T11:22:33.000Z","msg":"高登真係輸到貼地。"},{"pid":"6410590c87edc3f8022362b4e08e8ddfd297081c","tid":1178364,"uid":139700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T11:38:03.000Z","msg":"大灣駒認證連登都係廢人及社會垃圾"},{"pid":"c8254ab330a63489ee3370f11fd68920384df